<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Jeremy Okmen — Portfolio</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #1c1a15;
    --dark: #242018;
    --mid: #2e2a1f;
    --card: #2a2619;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e2c27d;
    --white: #f5f0e8;
    --grey: #a09880;
    --border: rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* CUSTOM CURSOR */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transition: transform 0.35s ease, width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(28,26,21,0.97), transparent);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--gold); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 60px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 40%, rgba(201,168,76,0.16) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(201,168,76,0.10) 0%, transparent 50%),
      var(--black);
  }
  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    animation: gridpulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes gridpulse {
    0%,100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .hero-photo-placeholder {
    position: absolute;
    right: 60px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 380px;
    height: 500px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--grey);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: fadeup 1s ease 0.3s both;
  }
  .hero-photo-placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .photo-label { color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.5; font-size: 0.7rem; }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 620px; }
  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    animation: fadeup 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    animation: fadeup 0.8s ease 0.15s both;
  }
  .hero-name em { color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
    max-width: 480px;
    animation: fadeup 0.8s ease 0.3s both;
  }
  .hero-line {
    width: 60px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 32px 0;
    animation: expandline 1s ease 0.6s both;
  }
  @keyframes expandline { from { width: 0; } to { width: 60px; } }
  .hero-scroll {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--grey);
    animation: fadeup 0.8s ease 0.5s both;
  }
  .scroll-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes bounce { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(6px)} }
  @keyframes fadeup {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 100px 60px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about { background: var(--dark); }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-text p strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stat-box {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .stat-box:hover { background: var(--mid); }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--grey);
  }

  /* SKILLS */
  .skills { background: var(--black); }
  .skills-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
  }
  .skill-group h3 {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .skill-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .skill-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .skill-item span { font-size: 0.92rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.8); }
  .work-item {
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .work-icon {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .work-item span { font-size: 0.92rem; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* EXPERIENCE */
  .experience { background: var(--dark); }
  .exp-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .exp-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .exp-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 4px; height: 100%;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .exp-org {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .exp-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .exp-body {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .exp-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .tag {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--grey);
  }

  /* OPLEIDING */
  .opleiding { background: var(--black); }
  .edu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .edu-card {
    padding: 36px;
    background: var(--card);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .edu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .edu-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .edu-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
  }

  /* TOEKOMST */
  .toekomst {
    background: var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .toekomst .section-title { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .toekomst .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .future-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .future-card {
    padding: 40px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .future-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04);
  }
  .future-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; right: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .future-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .future-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
  }

  /* TROTS */
  .trots { background: var(--black); }
  .trots-inner {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .trots-inner::after {
    content: '★';
    position: absolute;
    right: 48px;
    bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 8rem;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .trots-inner p {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 700px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.85);
  }
  .trots-inner .author {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* CONTACT / FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 80px 60px 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .footer-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .footer-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .footer-name span { color: var(--gold); }
  .footer-info p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.6);
  }
  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--grey);
  }
  .gold { color: var(--gold); }

  /* PHOTO SECTION */
  .photos { background: var(--mid); }
  .photo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .photo-slot {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--grey);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }
  .photo-slot:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
  }
  .photo-slot::before {
    content: '⬚';
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  }

  /* SCROLL ANIMATIONS */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hero { padding: 0 24px 60px; }
    .hero-photo-placeholder { display: none; }
    section { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .about-grid, .skills-layout, .edu-grid, .future-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .photo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .footer-top { flex-direction: column; gap: 32px; }
    .exp-card { padding: 28px; }
    .trots-inner { padding: 36px 28px; }
    footer { padding: 60px 24px 40px; }
  }

  /* ACCORDION GALLERY */
  .photo-grid-accordion {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .accordion-item {
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .accordion-item:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .accordion-item.open { border-color: var(--gold); }
  .accordion-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .accordion-img-wrap img {
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-img-wrap img,
  .accordion-item.open .accordion-img-wrap img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
  .accordion-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(13,13,13,0.35);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-overlay { opacity: 1; }
  .accordion-item.open .accordion-overlay { opacity: 1; }
  .accordion-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
    display: block;
  }
  .accordion-item.open .accordion-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .accordion-body {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.5s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
    padding: 0 24px;
    background: var(--card);
  }
  .accordion-item.open .accordion-body {
    max-height: 220px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .accordion-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .accordion-text {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .photo-grid-accordion { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }


  .mercedes-showcase {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .mercedes-img {
    width: 65%;
    max-width: 680px;
    display: block;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 50px rgba(201,168,76,0.2));
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .mercedes-img { width: 95%; } }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Cursor -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Jeremy Okmen</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#over">Over mij</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#stage">Stage</a></li>
    <li><a href="#opleiding">Opleiding</a></li>
    <li><a href="#toekomst">Toekomst</a></li>
    <li><a href="#fotos">Foto's</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-photo-placeholder" style="border:none;padding:0;overflow:hidden;background:none;">
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Jeremy Okmen" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top;display:block;">
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">Marketing & Communicatie · Fotograaf · Content Creator</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Jeremy<br><em>Okmen</em></h1>
    <div class="hero-line"></div>
    <p class="hero-sub">Creatief, visueel sterk en gedreven. Ik zet ideeën om in beelden, verhalen en resultaten — en doe dat elke dag met meer scherpte.</p>
    <div class="hero-scroll">
      <div class="scroll-dot"></div>
      Scroll om te ontdekken
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OVER MIJ -->
<section class="about" id="over">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">01 — Over mij</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Wie ben ik?</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <p>Mijn naam is <strong>Jeremy Okmen</strong>. Ik studeer Marketing & Communicatie en combineer dat met een groeiende passie voor fotografie, video en content creatie. De voorbije jaren heb ik mezelf sterk ontwikkeld — zowel in vakkennis als in mindset.</p>
      <p>Door bewust te kiezen waar ik mijn energie in steek, heb ik geleerd wat het betekent om <strong>gefocust en georganiseerd</strong> te werken. Je omgeving vormt je — dat inzicht heeft mijn manier van denken en werken fundamenteel veranderd.</p>
      <p>Vandaag sta ik klaar om <strong>verantwoordelijkheid op te nemen</strong> binnen een professionele omgeving. Ik werk zelfstandig, denk oplossingsgericht en ben altijd op zoek naar de volgende stap vooruit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stats reveal">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <span class="stat-num">2e</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Jaar Marketing & Communicatie</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <span class="stat-num">2–3</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Eigen projecten in ontwikkeling</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <span class="stat-num">∞</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Groeimindset</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <span class="stat-num">1</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Elke dag scherper worden</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section class="skills" id="skills">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">02 — Competenties</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Sterktes &<br>werkpunten</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="skills-layout">
    <div class="skill-group reveal">
      <h3>Sterktes</h3>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Sterk communicatief en sociaal vaardig</span></div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Creatief — van concept tot uitvoering</span></div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Technisch vaardig — Adobe, video, web</span></div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Snel inzetbaar in elk team</span></div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Rustig onder druk, stressbestendig</span></div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-dot"></div><span>Scherp oog voor visueel detail</span></div>
    </div>
